data.description: Welcome to your very own slice of country paradise in the heart of Ocala – a unique oasis where farm-style living meets versatility! This one-of-a-kind pool home, complete with a detached studio, is a true gem in the ever-growing city. Imagine yourself in a property where every detail has been carefully considered for a down-to-earth and comfortable lifestyle.  The main components of this house, including the AC and roof have been recently upgraded ensuring not just comfort but peace of mind. Picture lazy afternoons spent by the shimmering pool, creating memories that last a lifetime! Step into the Florida room, a cozy haven equipped with a wood heater to keep you warm on those rare chilly nights in Ocala. This space is not just a room; it's a retreat, a place where you can unwind and connect with the beauty of your surroundings.  This property is a haven for those seeking a farm-type living experience. Yet, it holds even more potential for savvy investors. Imagine house hacking your way to financial success – turning this residence into a money-making property with its strategic layout and proximity to the equestrian center and nearby springs! cha-ching!  Seize the opportunity to own a slice of Ocala's country charm, where modern living meets farm-style comfort and financial opportunity that is sitting on 1.07 acres !  This property is not just a house; it's a canvas for your dreams and a gateway to a lifestyle of down-to-earth luxury. Welcome home!
